Uses of Package
com.appreflector.common

  • Classes in com.appreflector.common used by com.appreflector.common 
    Class and Description
    FXWebApp
    FXWebApp is used to embed a JavaFX scene into a browser and support user interaction via JavaScript callbacks in the host environment.
    FXWebApp.FXWebWindow
    FXWebWindow subclass of FXWebApp that provides support for JavaFX scenes outside of the hosting Web document.
    FXWebAppControllerInterface
    Interface for controllers used by an FXWebApp.
    HostUtilitiesInterface
    Classes implementing this interface can be used from the host context by calling the getUtil method on an FXWebApp instance.
